{"tid":2203980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港地形豐富　地名用字多變　灣角嘴林涌澳灘湖塘窩盆椏","createTime":"2020-09-15T17:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T05:19:10.000Z","uid":261647,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5968e0b1658c6d3bdc92e24a776e50b3ccfac835","tid":2203980,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:05:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TheCommonMap/photos/a.138096431029171/186256572879823/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTheCommonMap%2Fphotos%2Fa.138096431029171%2F186256572879823%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=b03a4273\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TheCommonMap/photos/a.138096431029171/186256572879823/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Vujsu9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Vujsu9.jpg&h=9c9f9b79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不畫不知, 地名同地形的關係<br />\n以後行山郊遊， 聽到個名就幻想到條路／ 個景喇！<br />\n<br />\n繼上次發現慶春約七村嘅通名 (最後嗰隻描述地理嘅字)個個唔同，<br />\n市區地名似乎來來去去都係「灣」、「角」、「嘴」，只係因為我哋立足嘅都係從前臨海，現在填海嘅土地上。<br />\n<br />\n反觀鄉郊村落都係依山傍水(先揾到食)，名稱都係好確切有山有水嘅地形景觀呢。期待發掘更多後以香港嘅豐富地形，出個山系水系土系地名圖!"},{"pid":"0803852970d6acd9ec4d0c471ccd3500755d3e77","tid":2203980,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:07:00.000Z","msg":"好正張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一目了然"},{"pid":"7d5aade657ccab75060934aa0b8c64d10aeb6d60","tid":2203980,"uid":345689,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"學到嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3906d4c93d5108969bab02f18d58040c500cc8","tid":2203980,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:35:54.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2208f9684c0c0e17a264e8663219c1aa00441598","tid":2203980,"uid":15730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"reply